      "writtenOn": "2017-11-06T18:06:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The main intended purpose is so that stencilPath, stencilRect, StencilPathArgs, et. al. can accept a GrHardClip instead of GrClip. This guarantees at compile time that we won\u0027t accidentally try to clip a draw to stencil using coverage FPs.\n\nThe assert is just so we can cast it up to a regular GrClip.",
